nt of them. Walden, Jr. was charged and convicted of rape and sentenced to 75 years in prison. On Nov. 18, 1965, after serving 14 years of his sentence, Walden, Jr. was granted parole. On Jan. 13, 2003 Walden, Jr. received a pardon of innocence.
